{# packs/events-management/templates/vip-handling-checklist.md.j2
   Jinja2 template for the VIP handling checklist posted to event-team-slack.
   Rendered by registration-triage when is_vip = true.
   Posted immediately (no HOTL gate) as a Slack notification.

   Context variables:
     registration.id            — registration UUID
     registration.name          — VIP registrant full name
     registration.email         — VIP registrant email
     registration.tier          — 'vip' (always, by this point)
     registration.status        — 'confirmed' | 'waitlisted'
     registration.vip_reason    — 'tier_field' | 'domain_match'
     registration.dietary_needs       — list of normalised tags
     registration.accessibility_needs — list of normalised tags
     registration.registered_at  — registration timestamp
     event.name                 — event name
     event.starts_at            — event start datetime
     capacity_override          — boolean (true if VIP bypassed capacity)
     triage_notes               — optional free text from agent
#}

**VIP Registration Alert** — {{ event.name }}

A new VIP registrant has been processed and requires white-glove handling.

---

**Registrant**

| Field        | Value |
|--------------|-------|
| Name         | {{ registration.name }} |
| Email        | {{ registration.email }} |
| Status       | {{ registration.status | upper }} |
| VIP signal   | {{ registration.vip_reason | replace('_', ' ') | title }} |
| Registered   | {{ registration.registered_at | datetime_format('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M UTC') }} |

{% if capacity_override %}
> ⚠️ **Capacity override applied** — this VIP was confirmed despite the event
> being at or above capacity. Please verify this is intentional.

{% endif %}
{% if registration.dietary_needs %}
**Dietary needs:** {{ registration.dietary_needs | join(', ') }}
{% endif %}
{% if registration.accessibility_needs %}
**Accessibility needs:** {{ registration.accessibility_needs | join(', ') }}
{% endif %}
{% if triage_notes %}
**Triage notes:** {{ triage_notes }}
{% endif %}

---

**Handling Checklist**

Please complete the following before the event:

- [ ] Send personalised welcome email (use speaker-outreach-drafter or custom)
- [ ] Assign a dedicated event team point of contact for this VIP
- [ ] Reserve preferred seating / table if applicable
- [ ] Confirm dietary and accessibility arrangements with the venue
{% if registration.dietary_needs %}
  - Dietary: {{ registration.dietary_needs | join(', ') }}
{% endif %}
{% if registration.accessibility_needs %}
  - Accessibility: {{ registration.accessibility_needs | join(', ') }}
{% endif %}
- [ ] Add to VIP-only communications list (briefings, exclusive sessions)
- [ ] Ensure badge printing includes VIP designation
- [ ] Brief on-site staff on VIP's name and preferences
- [ ] Post-event: send thank-you note within 48 hours

---

Registration ID: `{{ registration.id }}`
Event starts: {{ event.starts_at | datetime_format('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M UTC') }}
